comment: Harden (HOU) makes marginal contact with Jokic (DEN) that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Jokic (DEN) directs the ball away from the official after the whistle.
Chandler (DEN) makes contact with Harden (HOU) that affects his SQBR.
Harden (HOU) legally contests Jokic's (DEN) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Nene (HOU) and Chandler (DEN) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Gallinari (DEN) legally contests Harden's (HOU) jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of HOU possession stands.
Harris (DEN) makes incidental contact with Harden (HOU) that does not affect his SQBR.
Ariza (HOU) makes contact with Jokic (DEN) that affects his FOM.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that the foul committed by Ariza (HOU) occured prior to the inbound pass, and Ariza is assessed an away from the play foul.
Jokic (DEN) grabs and pulls Nene's (HOU) jersey away from his body.
Gallinari (DEN) makes contact to Harden's (HOU) arm that affects his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Nelson (DEN) moves his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Beverley (HOU) following the screen.
Beverley (HOU) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Gallinari (DEN), who extends his legs to initiate the contact.
Chandler (DEN) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
[Observable in enhanced video] Harden (HOU) never fully clears the lane and is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Nelson (DEN) commits a take foul on Gordon (HOU).
